author: The Babylon Bee
description:
Ladies, sometimes you just have to tell your husband something completely irrelevant involving people he doesn't really know, or things that don't pertain to him. The important thing is knowing when is the right time to do it.

URGENT CHRISTMAS NEED: @ConvoyofHope needs 12 more people right now to sponsor chickens for poor families around the world. Let them have hope this Christmas: https://convoyofhope.org/bbee/
title: Best Times To Make Your Husband To Pay Attention To You
